### AR-002-002: CodeInterpreterList type definition\n33: \n34: - **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreter` type is defined\n35: - **WHEN** defining `CodeInterpreterList` struct\n36: - **THEN** the type SHALL embed `metav1.TypeMeta` with `json:\",inline\"` tag\n37: - **AND** SHALL embed `metav1.ListMeta` with `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"` tag\n38: - **AND** SHALL include `Items` field of type `[]CodeInterpreter` with `json:\"items\"` tag\n39: - **AND** SHALL have `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` marker\n40: \n41: ### AR-002-003: CodeInterpreterSpec fields\n42: \n43: - **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterSpec` struct definition\n44: - **WHEN** defining spec fields\n45: - **THEN** `AuthMode` SHALL be of type `AuthMode` (enum: \"picod\", \"none\"), optional, default `\"picod\"`\n46: - **AND** `MaxSessionDuration` SHALL be `string` type, optional, default `\"8h\"`\n47: - **AND** `SessionTimeout` SHALL be `string` type, optional, default `\"15m\"`\n48: - **AND** `Ports` SHALL be `[]TargetPort` type, optional\n49: - **AND** `Template` SHALL be of type `ContainerTemplateSpec`, required\n50: - **AND** `WarmPoolSize` SHALL be `int32` type, optional, default `0`\n51: \n52: ### AR-002-004: CodeInterpreterStatus with ready field\n53: \n54: - **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterStatus` struct definition\n55: - **WHEN** defining status subresource\n56: - **THEN** it SHALL include `Conditions` of type `[]metav1.Condition` with `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"` tag\n57: - **AND** SHALL include `ObservedGeneration` of type `int64` with `json:\"observedGeneration,omitempty\"` tag\n58: - **AND** SHALL include `Ready` of type `bool` with `json:\"ready\"` tag\n59: \n60: ### AR-002-005: Supporting types definition\n61: \n62: - **GIVEN** CodeInterpreter types are defined\n63: - **WHEN** defining supporting types\n64: - **THEN** `TargetPort` SHALL include `Port` (int32), `Protocol` (HTTP/HTTPS), `Name`, `PathPrefix` fields\n65: - **AND** `ContainerTemplateSpec` SHALL include `Image` (required), `Command`, `Args`, `Env`, `Resources`, `RuntimeClassName` fields\n66: - **AND** `AuthMode` SHALL be defined as a string type with constants `AuthModePicod` and `AuthModeNone`\n67: \n68: ### AR-002-006: DeepCopy method generation\n69: \n70: - **GIVEN** CodeInterpreter types are defined in `types.go`\n71: - **WHEN** running deepcopy generation\n72: - **THEN** `CodeInterpreter.DeepCopyInto(*CodeInterpreter)` SHALL be generated\n73: - **AND** `CodeInterpreter.DeepCopy() *CodeInterpreter` SHALL be generated\n74: - **AND** `CodeInterpreter.DeepCopyObject() runtime.Object` SHALL be generated\n75: - **AND** `CodeInterpreterList.DeepCopyInto(*CodeInterpreterList)` SHALL be generated\n76: - **AND** `CodeInterpreterList.DeepCopy() *CodeInterpreterList` SHALL be generated\n77: - **AND** `CodeInterpreterList.DeepCopyObject() runtime.Object` SHALL be generated\n78: - **AND** `CodeInterpreterSpec.DeepCopyInto(*CodeInterpreterSpec)` SHALL be generated\n79: - **AND** `CodeInterpreterSpec.DeepCopy() *CodeInterpreterSpec` SHALL be generated\n80: - **AND** `CodeInterpreterStatus.DeepCopyInto(*CodeInterpreterStatus)` SHALL be generated\n81: - **AND** `CodeInterpreterStatus.DeepCopy() *CodeInterpreterStatus` SHALL be generated\n82: \n83: ---\n84: \n85: ## References\n86: \n87: - Base spec: `deployment/client-go.md`\n88: - AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n89: - API Group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n90: - Version: `v1alpha1`\n\n(End of file - total 90 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Spec: AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n\n## Overview\n\nThis delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the CodeInterpreter CRD type definitions in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`.\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-002\n- **Module**: `pkg/apis`\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: S\n- **Base Spec**: `deployment/client-go.md` (client-go library types)\n\n---\n\n## Scenario: CodeInterpreter Type Definition\n\n### AR-002-001: CodeInterpreter type definition\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspa